item.title: About
item.dc:creator: Emiles
item.content:encoded: Old Hillsboro Building Company, LLC is a landdevelopment and construction company building residential and commercial properties in the beautiful countryside of Tennessee. The company wasformed by a seasoned custom builder, who has been creatinghigh-end, residential and commercial properties in the middle Tennessee area for over 24 years. We select beautiful properties and then work with a team ofexperienceddesigners and high-quality craftsmen to create a product we think you will love. If you are looking for a propertyin the peaceful hills of middle Tennessee,contactusto see what we have available and what's coming next!
